sections.heading: Warrants; specify fund upon which drawn
sections.text: Each warrant issued shall specify the fund upon which it is drawn.SourceLaws 1879, § 35, p. 365;R.S.1913, § 963;C.S.1922, § 863;C.S.1929, § 26-117;Laws 1939, c. 23, § 1, p. 123;C.S.Supp.,1941, § 26-117;R.S.1943, § 23-133;Laws 1963, c. 110, § 1, p. 438.Annotati
